    "description": "Mphasis Digital Technologies has an exciting opening for a Backend Developer at our Jodhpur office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Mphasis Digital Technologies:\nMphasis Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mphasis Digital Technologies!",
